    <label>Karibito no Omamori</label>
    <description>\nThe Kariudo no Omamori is a symbol of power. With wisdom, power can bring balance; with hate, power will bring only destruction. The Pekodra are to be feared, yes, but they also serve as guardians at times, protecting villages without their knowledge: this service was nearly lost. The legacy of this bloodlust infects such charms, making it far more difficult to train or tame animals while wearing one. So, what shall this amulet mean for your village?</description>
